            overview: "Lasso (Least Absolute Shrinkage and Selection Operator) adds L1 regularization: minimize MSE + alpha * sum(|w_i|). This penalty forces some coefficients to be exactly zero, performing automatic feature selection. Lasso produces sparse, interpretable models.",
